{"tid":424074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈大師預言：升多1100點 港股就到頂！","createTime":"2017-10-04T11:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T02:02:34.000Z","uid":37380,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b194d97230b8661531dd52e0f74ab465e3fecc","tid":424074,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"內地股市止跌，港股形勢大好，今日又升200點，創近兩年高位。人稱沈大師的訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈認為，恒指短期會在25,200點附近調整，「6、7月估計再會升多一浸就差唔多啦，成個浪就差唔多啦今年」，樂觀來看浪頂可能在26,200點。以現時恒指25100水平，即潛在升幅約1100點。<br />\n<br />\n沈大師昨日建議買落後的內銀股，今日有不錯的升幅。他指，內銀內險股最值博，直至6、7月份會跑羸大市，「甚至會跑贏騰訊（700）添&hellip;騰訊個升幅跟住會慢。」另外，有傳「債券通」將於7月推出，沈大師中長期唔太睇好港交所（388），「借嚟炒一轉冇所謂，如果炒到200蚊樓上就係唔合理囉，算係貴。」<br />\n<br />\n沈大師昨日接受本報訪問時表示，「我當佢係短期升浪，唔可以話確認，短期我會覺得博完呢浸再算&hellip;擔心係最後升浪，因為到六月後，開始又再加息，之後炒縮表，嗰啲會第三、四季發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170510/56675031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170510%2F56675031&d=frl0UrnvNjjxBuJ1bdA3sgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e35dbee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170510%2F56675031&h=a5744f4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170510/56675031</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f8f3c93e06ae5163d5088839945a942f43ca3f","tid":424074,"uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要all in牛牛了！"},{"pid":"d56af6df11e396ee02b2ad94f8739e1c30ae5d35","tid":424074,"uid":37380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji